Package: geoclue-2.0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: geoinformation service
 GeoClue is a D-Bus geoinformation service. The goal of the Geoclue project
 is to make creating location-aware applications as simple as possible.
 .
 This package contains the D-Bus system service for GeoClue.

Package: geoclue-2.0-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: geoclue-2.0 (= ${binary:Version}),
         libglib2.0-dev (>= 2.34.0),
         libjson-glib-dev (>= 0.14),
         libsoup2.4-dev,
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Geographic information framework (development files)
 GeoClue provides applications access to various geographical information
 sources using a D-Bus API.
 .
 This package contains the master server for GeoClue.
